data.description: This 4 bedroom, master on main home provides the perfect layout for any stage in life. The two-story foyer opens to a spacious family room with open concept breakfast area and kitchen. The large master suite offers a luxurious bath with walk-in shower, tub and dual vanities for plenty of space. This space also includes a large, walk-in closet.  Upstairs, this plan includes a spacious media room perfect for entertaining guests or a game area for the kids.
